''AKA Grab Sampling, Accidental Sampling, Opportunity Sampling''

This happens when you sample whatever is easy to reach, ignoring the hard to reach parts of the [[Population|Population (Statistics)]], thus making your [[Sample|Sample (Statistics)]] not really random.